- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper deals with evolutionary algorithms and optimization problems. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper discusses the performance of an algorithm on different functions. 
- cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory) is less likely but still possible as the paper deals with optimization problems and fitness landscapes, which are relevant to game theory.
